message.content: Who’d endured an undue period of repression, the voice went on to describe the beauty of the Tibetan colony in Sussex, in all its obscene details. Then the radio went dead again, and Peter had no stomach for breakfast. It was a beautiful day, at fiddler-of-June should be. There got out the car and traversed the same empty streets as she had the night before, to keep an appointment with Feather.
